trans-unit.source: You can also call setException() to replace the thrown exception. This exception will be thrown if no response is set during processing of this event.
trans-unit.target: 你也可以调用setException()来替换抛出的异常。如果在处理该事件的过程中没有设置响应,则会抛出该异常。

trans-unit.source: You can also optionally pass a {@link CacheInterface} instance to the constructor. This cache will be used for persisting the generated metadata between multiple PHP requests.
trans-unit.target: 你也可以选择传递一个{@link CacheInterface}实例到构造函数中。这个缓存将用于在多个PHP请求之间持久化生成的元数据。

trans-unit.source: You can also wrap the iterator into a {@link \RecursiveIteratorIterator} to flatten the recursive structure into a flat list of errors.
trans-unit.target: 你也可以将迭代器包装成{@link \RecursiveIteratorIterator},将递归结构扁平化为一个扁平的错误列表。

trans-unit.source: You can call getController() to retrieve the controller and getArguments to retrieve the current arguments. With setArguments() you can replace arguments that are used to call the controller.
trans-unit.target: 你可以调用getController()来检索控制器,调用getArguments来检索当前的参数。通过setArguments(),你可以替换用于调用控制器的参数。

trans-unit.source: You can call getController() to retrieve the current controller. With setController() you can set a new controller that is used in the processing of the request.
trans-unit.target: 你可以调用getController()来检索当前控制器。通过setController(),你可以设置一个新的控制器,用于处理请求。

trans-unit.source: You can call getResponse() to retrieve the current response. With setResponse() you can set a new response that will be returned to the browser.
trans-unit.target: 你可以调用getResponse()来检索当前的响应。通过setResponse(),你可以设置一个新的响应,并返回给浏览器。

trans-unit.source: You can call the method stopPropagation() to abort the execution of further listeners in your event listener.
trans-unit.target: 你可以调用方法stopPropagation()来中止事件监听器中进一步的监听器的执行。

trans-unit.source: You can either pass an existing database connection as PDO instance or a Doctrine DBAL Connection or a DSN string that will be used to lazy-connect to the database when the cache is actually used.
trans-unit.target: 你可以传递一个现有的数据库连接作为PDO实例,也可以传递一个Doctrine DBAL连接或一个DSN字符串,当缓存被实际使用时,它将被用于懒惰连接到数据库。

trans-unit.source: You can either pass an existing database connection as PDO instance or pass a DSN string that will be used to lazy-connect to the database when the session is actually used. Furthermore it's possible to pass null which will then use the session.save_path ini setting as PDO DSN parameter.
trans-unit.target: 你可以传入一个现有的数据库连接作为PDO实例,或者传入一个DSN字符串,当实际使用会话时,这个DSN字符串将被用来懒惰连接到数据库。此外,也可以传入null,然后使用session.save_path ini设置作为PDO DSN参数。

trans-unit.source: You can optionally pass a {@link LoaderInterface} instance to the constructor. Whenever a new metadata instance is created, it is passed to the loader, which can configure the metadata based on configuration loaded from the filesystem or a database. If you want to use multiple loaders, wrap them in a {@link LoaderChain}.
trans-unit.target: 你可以选择性地将{@link LoaderInterface}实例传递给构造函数。每当创建一个新的元数据实例时,它都会被传递给加载器,加载器可以根据从文件系统或数据库加载的配置来配置元数据。如果你想使用多个加载器,可以将它们包裹在一个{@link LoaderChain}中。

trans-unit.source: You need to define an implementation for the getRouteDefaults() method. Most of the time, this method should define some PHP callable to be called for the route (a controller in MVC speak).
trans-unit.target: 你需要为getRouteDefaults()方法定义一个实现。大多数情况下,这个方法应该定义一些PHP可调用的路由(MVC中的控制器)。

trans-unit.source: You should always use this method when overwriting existing arguments of the parent definition.
trans-unit.target: 当覆盖父定义的现有参数时,您应该始终使用此方法。

trans-unit.source: You should make sure a valid value is passed to the option.
trans-unit.target: 你应该确保传递给选项的是一个有效的值。

trans-unit.source: You should never use an empty domain, but if you do so, all cookies for the given name/path expire (this behavior ensures a BC behavior with previous versions of Symfony).
trans-unit.target: 你永远不应该使用空域名,但如果你这样做,所有给定的名称/路径的cookie都会过期(这种行为确保了以前版本的Symfony的BC行为)。
